<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>QuickBites - Online Food Ordering</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; margin: 0; }
        header { background-color: #ff5722; color: white; padding: 1rem; text-align: center; }
        nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; background: #ff7043; padding: 0.5rem; }
        nav a { color: white; margin: 0 1rem; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
        section { padding: 2rem; max-width: 1200px; margin: auto; }
        .restaurant { background: white; padding: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .menu-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; }
        .menu-item img { width: 60px; height: 60px; border-radius: 8px; margin-right: 1rem; }
        .cart { background: #fff3e0; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px; }
        .btn { background-color: #ff5722; color: white; border: none; padding: 0.5rem 1rem; cursor: pointer; border-radius: 4px; }
        footer { text-align: center; padding: 1rem; background: #eee; margin-top: 2rem; }
        .payment-options { margin-top: 1rem; }
        .payment-options label { margin-right: 1rem; }
        .payment-details { margin-top: 1rem; }
        .payment-details input { display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; padding: 0.5rem; width: 100%; max-width: 300px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>QuickBites</h1>
        <p>Your favorite food delivered fast!</p>
    </header>
    <nav>
        <a href="#restaurants">Restaurants</a>
        <a href="#cart">Cart</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
    <section id="restaurants">
        <h2>Available Restaurants</h2>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Seafood Delight</h3>
            <p>Fresh seafood with authentic flavors.</p>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Grilled Salmon">
                <span>Grilled Salmon</span>
                <button class="btn" onclick="addToCart('Grilled Salmon')">Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Fried Prawns">
                <span>Fried Prawns</span>
                <button class="btn" onclick="addToCart('Fried Prawns')">Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," alt="Octopus Salad">
                <span>Octopus Salad</span>
                <button class="btn" onclick="addToCart('Octopus Salad')">Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="restaurant">
            <h3>Urban Bites</h3>
            <p>Modern fusion cuisine for every taste.</p>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/60?text=Burger" alt="Chicken Burger">
                <span>Chicken Burger</span>
                <button class="btn" onclick="addToCart('Chicken Burger')">Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/60?text=Noodles" alt="Spicy Noodles">
                <span>Spicy Noodles</span>
                <button class="btn" onclick="addToCart('Spicy Noodles')">Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
            <div class="menu-item">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/60?text=Wrap" alt="Veg Wrap">
                <span>Veg Wrap</span>
                <button class="btn" onclick="addToCart('Veg Wrap')">Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section id="cart">
        <h2>Your Cart</h2>
        <div class="cart" id="cart-items">
            <p>No items in the cart.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="payment-options">
            <h3>Select Payment Method</h3>
            <label><input type="radio" name="payment" value="Credit/Debit Card" checked onclick="showPaymentDetails()"> Credit/Debit Card</label>
            <label><input type="radio" name="payment" value="UPI" onclick="showPaymentDetails()"> UPI</label>
            <label><input type="radio" name="payment" value="Wallet" onclick="showPaymentDetails()"> Wallet</label>
        </div>
        <div class="payment-details" id="payment-details">
            <!-- Payment fields will appear here -->
        </div>
        <button class="btn" onclick="checkout()">Proceed to Payment</button>
    </section>
    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Email: quickbites2000@gmail.com</p>
        <p>Phone: +91 9876543210</p>
    </section>
    <footer>
        &copy; 2025 QuickBites. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
    <script>
        const cart = [];

        function addToCart(item) {
            cart.push(item);
            updateCart();
        }

        function updateCart() {
            const cartDiv = document.getElementById('cart-items');
            if (cart.length === 0) {
                cartDiv.innerHTML = '<p>No items in the cart.</p>';
                return;
            }
            let html = '<ul>';
            cart.forEach((item, index) => {
                html += `<li>${item} <button onclick="removeFromCart(${index})">Remove</button></li>`;
            });
            html += '</ul>';
            cartDiv.innerHTML = html;
        }

        function removeFromCart(index) {
            cart.splice(index, 1);
            updateCart();
        }

        function showPaymentDetails() {
            const paymentMethod = document.querySelector('input[name="payment"]:checked').value;
            const detailsDiv = document.getElementById('payment-details');
            if (paymentMethod === 'Credit/Debit Card') {
                detailsDiv.innerHTML = `
                    <input type="text" id="card-number" placeholder="Card Number">
                    <input type="text" id="card-expiry" placeholder="Expiry Date (MM/YY)">
                    <input type="text" id="card-cvv" placeholder="CVV">
                `;
            } else if (paymentMethod === 'UPI') {
                detailsDiv.innerHTML = `
                    <input type="text" id="upi-id" placeholder="UPI ID">
                `;
            } else if (paymentMethod === 'Wallet') {
                detailsDiv.innerHTML = `
                    <input type="text" id="wallet-number" placeholder="Wallet Number">
                `;
            }
        }

        function checkout() {
            if (cart.length === 0) {
                alert('Your cart is empty!');
                return;
            }
            const paymentMethod = document.querySelector('input[name="payment"]:checked').value;
            let valid = true;
            if (paymentMethod === 'Credit/Debit Card') {
                const card = document.getElementById('card-number').value.trim();
                const expiry = document.getElementById('card-expiry').value.trim();
                const cvv = document.getElementById('card-cvv').value.trim();
                if (!card || !expiry || !cvv) {
                    valid = false;
                    alert('Please fill all card details.');
                }
            } else if (paymentMethod === 'UPI') {
                const upi = document.getElementById('upi-id').value.trim();
                if (!upi) {
                    valid = false;
                    alert('Please enter UPI ID.');
                }
            } else if (paymentMethod === 'Wallet') {
                const wallet = document.getElementById('wallet-number').value.trim();
                if (!wallet) {
                    valid = false;
                    alert('Please enter Wallet Number.');
                }
            }
            if (!valid) return;
            alert(`Payment successful using ${paymentMethod}! Your order is being processed.`);
            cart.length = 0; // Clear the cart
            updateCart();
            document.getElementById('payment-details').innerHTML = '';
        }

        window.onload = showPaymentDetails;
    </script>
</body>
</html>
